@NODE SC-Install "Installing GUIEnvironment for SAS/C"

Copy the interface modules (guienv.h, geclass.h and guienvsupport.h) to a
SAS/C include directory (e.g into the sc:include/libraries drawer).

Now the installation is complete and you can compile and run the
examples.

@ENDNODE

@NODE SC-Interface "The SAS/C interface module"

The SAS/C interface module contains all constants, structures and
functions explained in the documents.


@ENDNODE

@NODE SC-Support "GUIEnvSupport for SAS/C"

All functions explained in the GUIEnvironment support guide are
implemented here.


@ENDNODE

